high_descs: turn to face green kitchen island
pick up fork from the island
wash fork in sink, pick up fork from sink
turn to the right to face counter to the right of the sink
put the fork on the counter
anns.task_desc: put a washed fork onto a counter top

high_descs: Turn around and walk two steps then turn left to face the table.
Pick up the fork from the table that is behind the metal glass.
Turn around and walk to the sink.
Wash the fork off in the sink then pick it up.
Turn right to face the stove.
Put the fork on the counter next to the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean fork on the counter by the coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn around, walk forward to the center of the dining table and turn left to face it.
Pick up the fork on the dining table behind the wine glass.
Turn around and walk forward to the sink.
Put the fork in the sink, rinse it off, and take it back out.
Turn right towards the counter to the right of the sink.
Put the fork on the counter, to the left of the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned fork on a counter top.
